This repository contains documentation for the publicly accessible Bit Monk Signal
MCP endpoints. The documentation is provided as-is for the purpose of discovering
and integrating with these services.

The signal engine, indicator implementations, and data pipelines behind these
endpoints are proprietary and are not licensed or distributed here.

Use of the endpoints themselves is subject to their pay-per-call terms
(see README.md). The output is informational only and is not financial,
investment, or real-estate advice.
